{"tid":1926880,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"mythbuster教狗屎垃圾黑警點樣道歉，中國人社會好多狗屎垃圾係唔識道歉","createTime":"2020-03-15T11:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T12:52:42.000Z","uid":55725,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9d8286f307a9c1c472aceb12491e68f977841d","tid":1926880,"uid":55725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T11:47:34.000Z","msg":"科學呢，就係無絕對正確，係可以接受任何有料嘅人挑戰，就算牛頓、愛恩斯坦理論都有錯或者唔適用嘅時候<br />\n現今物理學極微細世界例如去到次原子粒子個種咁細嘅世界嘅時候，係用量子力學，愛恩斯坦相對論係用唔到<br />\n但係黑洞、星系、引力等場合就可以用愛恩斯坦相對論<br />\n<br />\n呢一集mythbuster因為科學實驗搞鳩咗人地屋企，佢地一開場係道歉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y4p1yGE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4p1yGE.png&h=7ac2169f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/inVPHz2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FinVPHz2.png&h=7a4d6296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pd0DAU4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPd0DAU4.png&h=fbe0aeda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BE89Hz6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBE89Hz6.png&h=c216cca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6WvDAU8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WvDAU8.png&h=bdbdecfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/897B61Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F897B61Q.png&h=1bfeab90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PduMKOy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPduMKOy.png&h=b439dfa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PbGLfVf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPbGLfVf.png&h=321b28ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awdmyGX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawdmyGX.pn